These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, zinnia, dahlia, poppy
1. the person who growszinnia is in an odd position##4
2. the person who growspoppy is between the person who growsazalea and the person who growszinnia##2
3. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Flower   | azalea | poppy | zinnia | dahlia |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, subway, motorbike, roller
1. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
2. the person driving the subway is in an odd position##4
3. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person driving the boat##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Transport   | subway | boat | roller | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  lawyer, analyst, engineer, freelancer
1. the freelancer is on the left or right of the lawyer##3
2. the lawyer is in an odd position##4
3. the engineer is between the freelancer and the analyst##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Job   | lawyer | freelancer | engineer | analyst |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, chess, baking, collecting
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
2. the person who's hobby is baking is in an even position##4
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person who's hobby is baking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |       3       |   4    |
| Hobby   | chess | hiking | collecting | baking |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, indie, pop, techno
1. the fan of gospel is in an even position##4
2. the fan of pop is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
3. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the fan of pop##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | techno | gospel | pop | indie |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-6::.
