.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-14::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, skydiving, woodworking, cooking
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is reading##3
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is cooking##3
4. the person who's hobby is cooking is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Hobby   | woodworking | cooking | reading | skydiving |

