.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, quad-bike, tram, roller
1. the person driving the quad-bike is the person driving the quad-bike##1
2. the person driving the roller is on the left or right of the person driving the tram##3
3. the person driving the tram is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person driving the helicopter is in an even position##4
5. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Transport   | tram | roller | quad-bike | helicopter |

