.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-20::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, yellow, orange, white
1. the person who likes orange is in an odd position##4
2. the person who likes white is on the left of the person who likes orange##1
3. the person who likes orange is on the left or right of the person who likes yellow##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |         2          |    3    |    4     |
| Color   | grey | white | orange | yellow |

 